      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to provide for research into the development of energy-efficient technologies and renewable energy technologies and to foster the introduction of energy-efficient technologies and renewable energy technologies into the marketplace, with the goal of reducing United States oil imports.</title>
